{"tid":1154114,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"勝利「雙手被綁繩押送」上移送車！ 兩眼無神一句話都說不出口","createTime":"2019-05-14T05:23:17.000Z","updateTime":"2019-05-14T07:02:30.000Z","uid":74065,"like":5,"dislike":6,"uniUserReply":15,"replies":[{"pid":"5ba365f2410837a233933a10d198286cbee19520","tid":1154114,"uid":74065,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-14T05:23:17.000Z","msg":"勝利「雙手被綁繩押送」上移送車！ 兩眼無神一句話都說不出口<br />\n<br />\n南韓藝人勝利14日一早現身首爾中央地方法院接受調查，一身黑色西裝裝扮和律師都是嚴肅的表情，有別於上次接受警方調查時停下來受訪宣布「會誠實接受調查的」，這次從頭到尾都一語不發，南韓時間下午1點半左右雙手被綁著走出。<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/EuTEY8K.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FEuTEY8K.png&h=769f2fe0&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/71PHWVt.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F71PHWVt.png&h=1ebdfe19&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/0oK8StS.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F0oK8StS.png&h=5deb1509&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n▲勝利14日現身首爾中央地方法院時一句話都沒說。<br />\n<br />\n勝利14日早上大約10點30分的時候出現在首爾中央地方法院，日前韓警以性買賣仲介、挪用Burning Sun公款、違反食品衛生法等罪嫌提出申請他的拘留令，南韓時間大約下午1點半左右時，他雙手被綁著走出法院，雙眼無神看起來相當憔悴，黑眼圈也非常深，從表情中完全看不出有任何情緒，就這樣一語不發地被押送上移送車，他的拘留結果最早14日晚間、最晚15日凌晨會出爐。<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/yq4XLOU.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fyq4XLOU.png&h=4641b282&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/2HfjY8Y.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F2HfjY8Y.png&h=6a805ee8&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/UKnuBVH.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FUKnuBVH.png&h=fea640a0&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n▲▼勝利14日離開法院時被綁著上押送車。<br />\n<br />\n另外，勝利原本僅涉嫌性買賣仲介、挪用Burning Sun公款、違反食品衛生法等，但日前又多了一條，在警方調查資金來往的時候發現他涉嫌性買賣，雖然他否認並強調到家中的援交妹只是單純的交往關係，而且本來就認識。但據《NEWS A》報導，警察已經確認了他在2015年進行至少3次性買賣的行為，不只確認了金融交易紀錄，同時那些女生都已經在陳述中坦白。<br />\n<br />\n個心好痛😭"},{"pid":"2ec47a022413d51d356faea7e843e6eb7004d693","tid":1154114,"uid":208486,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-14T05:23:47.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3337a11dadfdf690d1f5dbc533815ca67ce43ad7","tid":1154114,"uid":143093,"like":18,"dislike":0,"score":18,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-14T05:25:14.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/50ajZbo.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F50ajZbo.gif&h=c0841109&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"9195db8c8c1cefc80b7816a69256498646642b22","tid":1154114,"uid":45773,"like":16,"dislike":0,"score":16,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-14T05:25:39.000Z","msg":"勝利(已失敗)"},{"pid":"d63f0f106c2ab6955dc23be690b2fb9bd06f52e2","tid":1154114,"uid":33359,"like":17,"dislike":0,"score":17,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-05-14T05:30:11.000Z","msg":"勝利（已笠水）"},{"pid":"5ad22249f5f165f5fdd53f36496b4ecb2f475beb","tid":1154114,"uid":138138,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-14T05:39:17.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/entertainment/20150818/photo/bkn-20150818182143151-0818_00862_001_01b.jpg?20150818182522\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fentertainment%2F20150818%2Fphoto%2Fbkn-20150818182143151-0818_00862_001_01b.jpg%3F20150818182522&h=0b76c2e7&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"2ff6e7a49de69de2145d0658a3fe3f3c88d34fb4","tid":1154114,"uid":143093,"like":3,"dislike":2,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"d63f0f106c2ab6955dc23be690b2fb9bd06f52e2","tid":1154114,"uid":33359,"like":17,"dislike":0,"score":17,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-05-14T05:30:11.000Z","msg":"勝利（已笠水）"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-14T05:39:57.000Z","msg":"收皮啦傻鳩"},{"pid":"56c18ed1f3503869d69e259efaf96aa0f963e851","tid":1154114,"uid":4180,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-14T06:19:43.000Z","msg":"oppa<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{